very happy to be in finish, i dont expect that.. ufff, i hope i will find a more time for train for mexico, bye

Really good rally for me ;) cool head till the end. No big problems, only small mistakes. Tomek - incredible fight, thank you! KILLAZ - job done! Now time to short holiday. In Mexico I must be faster! Thanks WR.PL for a great rally!
very bad start again and again....every SS bad start +2sec
Dzieki wszystkim byl swietnie emocje niesamowite po rolce stracilem szanse na dobry wynik ale mimo to jestem zadowolny z calego rajdu do zobaczenia w meksyku:)
bardzo fajny rajd, super mod, podziekowania dla organizatorowz

Kolejny rajd do zapomnienia niestety, tempo kiepskie, po lekkim uderzeniu przednia lampa i awarii rozrusznika nie moglem zlapac rytmu i motywacji. Ciezki poczatek sezonu dla mnie i masa pracy do zrobienia. Dzieki WR i do zobaczenia Szwecjo.
Bad rally for me. Audio problems with my codriver makes me lost the concentration. I made a mistakes hitting a little bit a fence and the car was destroyed. Bad start in the championship.

We had generally a few big mistakes, but even though I cant go faster on the snow. Mayby its a setup thing or something with me, but on the snow its really difficult for me to make a good result. Hopefully this is the last winter rally in this season ;-)
well, at least we finished but thats all, I am still angry on myself cause of that mistake, but its rally and life, we will be much stronger on our strongest surface, see ya in Guanajuato ;)

I would really like to see some onboards from the frontrunners. I just don't get where I lose those huge amounts of time. I just made 2 mistakes. 1 in Vargasen2 and one here in the powerstage. Cost around 30sec. But I would really like to check where I lose the other 3-4 sec per km.
Good rally for us,i hope we will be at top5. We have some problems with setup at kuadonvaara, but at other ss it was good... Good fight with Patryk :) Kryglerson pecka :)
na bledach ucieklo okolo 10 sec. Na blanare w srodku rajdu wydzwonilem zrobilem 360 i pojechalem dalej :) Go Go Killaz
Thank you! Congrat to all who are in finish! I hope for TOP5... I made few stupid mistekes,which cost me a lot of time... See you again next time! Oikee
Yes. Nareszcie rajd pojechany ok. Tylko te kanciate odcinki to porazka! Brawo Patryk, I etap byla walka z Toba, a pozniej jak widac. Dzieki
Do rajdu zgloslem inny model Peugeota niz ten ktorym trenowalem, niestety juz bylo za pozno zeby poustawiac go. Miala byc walka o top 5, a tak to byla walka o byt. Marcin - hejter roku 2017!
first leg was bad. second leg very good. pb last stage

Finished in 9th place but I do not think I can hold this top 10 finish... Karlstad is now my least favorite stage in the history of RBR. Spectator safety!!! Don't stand a foot away from the landing of the jump!!!!
not bad time with the damage that have the car.all repair good :)
I'm happy with this, lot of 'small' mistakes but finish in one peace is good for me, thx

Na wstepie chcialem pogratulowac Patrykowi, jakis kosmos to jego tempo. Naszym celem byla meta i sie udalo:) Ogolnie jazda bardzo powolna ze wzgledu na to, ze chcialem pojawic sie na mecie bez SR tak jak mialo to miejsce na MONTE. Powodzenia reszczie;) Rally and Race !!!

Great stage. Again good time, although it felt not much faster than the other stages. I guess a lot of people are really driving the original stages from their brains and did a lot of training. I can't find another conclusion.

Jest meta i to jest chyba jedyny pozytyw w tym rajdzie. Na oesie Hof-Finnskog przytrafia sie rolka i w konsekwencji tego na nastpnym odcinku auto nie chcialo juz jechac jak trzeba. Te przygody zabraly gdzies ok 1minuty. Reszta odcinkow przyzwoicie. Mam nadzieje ze wpadnie chociaz jeden punkt...
Zaczynamy sezon od Szwcji i to chyba dobry poczatek. Po zmianie klasy z RC4 brak jeszcze pewnosci auta, ale jest potencjal. Organizacyjnie swietna robota, mod, konfiguracja odcinkow, super.
bieda straszna. zly jestem na siebie i tyle moge powiedziec. kozacki mod ;)
Rajd okupiony mnostwem bledow szkoda, ale fajna zabawa na sniegu :D Czekam na Meksyk, Ogranizatorom szacun za moda, do zobaczenia :)
I tried hard in day 2 and 3 cuting some seconds. Mistake from ss8 destroy my chance for good resoults, but mayby I catch 1 point ;). Thanks WR and see U on next one.

I don't belive to be here, I push at every stage on my own limit, it was crazy, but now I'm very happy. I thinh it's enought for podium. Tomek, Eneko, it's Your turn Guys! Thx for WR.Pl for AMAZING config and for other drivers for fight! Now go to Leon.

Awesome rally. Im impressed by my self. Crazy speed during the whole event and very good fight stage by stage with the rest of the drivers. Thanks to WR.PL for the effort to create this champ and rally! See you :)
Super to be here. I enjoy it, it was very fast and very good fight with others, thank you.
fuuuuh..... Finish - eto Horosho. Spasibo za Gonki, Bilo slo)l(ho. Vsem Uda4i. See U next Stage.
Pierwszy dzien za nami i nie jest najgorzej
jeden blad przekreslil wszystko :( szkoda gadac :) ale co tam , zimy nie lubimy i czuc juz cieplo meksyku :) pozdro :)
Pues aqui estamos... Rally acabado sin problemas ni ayudas. Muy largo, pero al final 9 de la categoria. Muy contentos para ser nuestro primer rally de nieve despues de tanto tiempo sin tocar el RBR-
sukcesem jest meta, a przejechane kilometry to kawal dobrej roboty. Dzieki :)
krety ten oes, nie mam pomyslu jak go jechac
very dark (( Bad vision.....2x Times hit in Walls snow... lost 3-4sec. Need finish.
do not like this stage... crash and spin. Car is demaged
fighting with the steering wheel. the car is impossible to drve on a straight line. have rear right suspension broke with many positive camber. i will try on the last stage fight with sergey

Very nice rally for our crew. The snow in the morning was really challenging and road was very slipery. Fortunately we had just few small mistakes that cost us about 5-10 seconds. Before rally we hoped for higher possition in overall classification but we are happy with our performance in class.
Finisas! Aciu organizatoriams ir visiems dalyvavusiems uz grazias kovas greicio dopuose. Iki susitikimo kituose etapuose!
Gal butu ir nieko jei ne dustogai dar pareikalave ir pagalbos. Sekmes

Good, clean rally, maybe just a little bit too much risk on the last stage. Good fight with Alexander, lets see how well Lotus is gonna be on gravel comparing with Porsche next time. Good luck all, thanks! :)
big crash in first right 90 and very big damage car, bad steering and grip for attack...lost 5sec maybe more.... ((( At last need to finish it.
